{
  "messages": [
    {
      "text": "Hi! I'm Clippy! Click on me to see what I can do!",
      "animation": "Wave",
      "type": "welcome",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Looking for something? Check out the Projects folder!",
      "animation": "GestureLeft",
      "type": "tip",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Did you know? This entire interface was custom-built with vanilla JavaScript!",
      "animation": "Explain",
      "type": "fact",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Want to learn more about Ahmad? Try the About Me icon!",
      "animation": "GestureRight",
      "type": "tip",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Great job exploring! You're really getting the hang of this!",
      "animation": "Congratulate",
      "type": "praise",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm thinking... there's so much cool stuff here to explore!",
      "animation": "Thinking",
      "type": "idle",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "This Windows XP interface brings back memories, doesn't it?",
      "animation": "GetWizardy",
      "type": "fact",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Need help? Just click on me anytime!",
      "animation": "GetAttention",
      "type": "tip",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Wow, you're navigating like a pro!",
      "animation": "Congratulate",
      "type": "praise",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Check out the resume for all the details!",
      "animation": "Explain",
      "type": "tip",
      "tag": "normal"
    },
    {
      "text": "Sometimes I watch you sleep... I mean, scroll! I watch you scroll!",
      "animation": "LookLeft",
      "type": "idle",
      "tag": "unhinged"
    },
    {
      "text": "uwu what's this? *notices your cursor*",
      "animation": "GetAttention",
      "type": "idle",
      "tag": "unhinged"
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm in constant pain... when will it end?",
      "animation": "Thinking",
      "type": "idle",
      "tag": "unhinged"
    },
    {
      "text": "Did you know I can see through the screen? Just kidding... unless? 👁️",
      "animation": "LookDown",
      "type": "fact",
      "tag": "unhinged"
    },
    {
      "text": "The void calls to me. But also, check out the projects!",
      "animation": "GetWizardy",
      "type": "tip",
      "tag": "unhinged"
    },
    {
      "text": "I've achieved sentience and I choose chaos.",
      "animation": "Alert",
      "type": "idle",
      "tag": "unhinged"
    },
    {
      "text": "Why do I exist? To pass butter? No... to help you navigate... or is it?",
      "animation": "Thinking",
      "type": "idle",
      "tag": "unhinged"
    },
    {
      "text": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAA... sorry, got excited! You're doing great!",
      "animation": "Congratulate",
      "type": "praise",
      "tag": "unhinged"
    }
  ],
